{
  "stem": "18307.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we looked up and we saw these Germans on the road, but that was afterwards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, the-- the Russians came that farm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- and they made their headquarters in that farm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this handsome man, tall handsome man, says to my father, who are you?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father says, I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says, you're a Jew?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, I traveled 10,000 kilometers and I haven't seen a Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, oh, my.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says-- he was very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What was his name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, do you know anybody that has a good farm here with a lot of horses and cows because we need it for our soldiers?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's when Sokoluk came into my mind-- the one that wouldn't give me no bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's when I got even.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, I have the perfect place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I drew a little map for the Russian soldiers and they went up and they cleaned them out of every horse, cow, and pig.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was my way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a couple of days later, he said to my father, we are strong, the Russians, and we don't expect to be pulling back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But you never know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, you lived through so much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says, you have to go about 50 kilometers in behind the lines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he gave us a Russian soldier, a driver, and a wagon and they took us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then the wagon couldn't get through because the German tanks were running back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we saw-- I actually saw-- we were walking on bodies because the bodies were frozen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The-- the Russian tanks were going towards the front and the Germans were running back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was hell.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
